            <ul class="bullet-list">
                <li><p><strong>PEACOAT</strong><br>Say ahoy to classic style with a <a href="{{ENV_HOSTNAME}}/shop/mens-clothing/mens-jackets-coats/Coat_style/Peacoat?id=3763">peacoat</a>. What is a peacoat? A peacoat is a double-breasted, short coat made of wool that was historically worn by sailors. Now, peacoats are a standard for fall/winter style. How do you wear a peacoat? Pair up your peacoat with a sweater and ripped jeans for a laidback look. Anchor your casual wardrobe with a men&rsquo;s peacoat this cold-weather season from brands including Calvin Klein and Michael Kors.</p></li>
                <li><p><strong>RAINCOAT</strong><br>Don&rsquo;t let a downpour dampen your style. Sport a <a href="{{ENV_HOSTNAME}}/shop/mens-clothing/mens-jackets-coats/Coat_style/Raincoat?id=3763">raincoat</a> made of water-resistant materials in inclement weather. How is a raincoat different from a rain jacket? A raincoat goes past the waist, while a rain jacket hits at the waist. Having a longer silhouette, a raincoat lends itself for dressier occasions calling for a suit or slacks. When stormy weather hits, stay dry and dapper in men&rsquo;s raincoats, available at Macy&rsquo;s.</p></li>
                <li><p><strong>PUFFER COAT</strong><br>Do you have a proper buffer against the cold? Showcasing a quilted and lightweight design that provides insulation, a <a href="{{ENV_HOSTNAME}}/shop/mens-clothing/mens-jackets-coats/Coat_style/Puffer?id=3763">puffer coat</a> is a must-get for winter. Want one that&rsquo;s trending? Check out puffer coats with bold prints and colorful metallics. Remember to scope out styles with plenty of pockets to stow away gloves and other cold-weather essentials. What do you link up with your puffer jacket? Pair up your puffer coat with jeans and a cozy sweater for a casual feel. Weather winter storms in men&rsquo;s puffer coats from Columbia, Tommy Hilfiger, Michael Kors and Calvin Klein.</p></li>
                <li><p><strong>TRENCH COAT</strong><br>Is rain predicted in the forecast? Tie up a sharp look with a <a href="{{ENV_HOSTNAME}}/shop/mens-clothing/mens-jackets-coats/Coat_style/Trenchcoat?id=3763">trench coat</a>.  What is a trench coat? A trench coat is a double-breasted, full-length coat, featuring a belted waist, storm flaps and tab closures at the cuffs. Traditionally, these khaki-colored coats were used for the military. Now, trench coats are a staple for lightweight layering and are available in an array of neutral colors. For added warmth, look for trench coats with removable liners. Punctuate your classic style this season with a men&rsquo;s trench coat from top brands like Michael Kors, Calvin Klein and London Fog.</p></li>
                <li><p><strong>OVERCOAT</strong><br>You&rsquo;ll never be underdressed in an overcoat. What is an <a href="{{ENV_HOSTNAME}}/shop/b/mens-overcoat?id=71835">overcoat</a> vs. a trench coat? An overcoat is a long wool coat that is typically worn over a suit. This coat is definitely designed more for looks, so in extreme weather you might want to layer a slim-fitting puffer vest or jacket underneath your overcoat. For a relaxed look, you can totally rock an overcoat with jeans and sneaks. If you really want to make a statement, sport a camel overcoat in lieu of the traditional gray, black and navy. Sharpen up your cold-weather look in men&rsquo;s overcoats from Lauren Ralph Lauren, London Fog and Tommy Hilfiger.</p></li>
                <li><p><strong>LEATHER COAT</strong><br>Want to look hot and be warm this winter? Score major style points with a leather coat this cold-weather season. How is a leather coat different from a leather jacket? Hitting below the waist, a leather coat is longer than a leather jacket and has more insulation. How do you luxe up this look? Scope out leather coats with fur details. From business casual to weekend fun, a leather coat will lend a cool vibe to your fall/winter lineup.</p></li>
                <li><p><strong>PARKA</strong><br>Conquer arctic blasts in a <a href="{{ENV_HOSTNAME}}/shop/mens-clothing/mens-jackets-coats/Coat_style/Parka?id=3763">parka</a> this winter. What is parka? A parka is a heavyweight, hooded coat designed to withstand the harsh elements of winter. For prime protection against snow and sleet, scope out waterproof parkas with high fill counts. What do you wear with your parka? To ensure that you&rsquo;re warm, sport plenty of layers with your parka. For streetwear style, opt for a men&rsquo;s parka with a fur hood. Stock up on thermal underwear and cozy sweaters for a more pleasant winter. Drive the cold away in men&rsquo;s parkas from your fave brands, like The North Face, Tommy Hilfiger and Marmot.</p></li>
                <li><p><strong>PACKABLE COAT</strong><br>Whether you&rsquo;re hiking or traveling, a packable coat is totally handy. A packable coat includes its own pouch for easier transport in backpacks and suitcases. Being lightweight, a packable puffer coat protects against the elements without being hefty. Check out packable coats with down fill and drawstring hoods for extra warmth. Have a bon voyage in a men&rsquo;s packable coats from Michael Kors, Columbia or Hawke & Co.</p></li>
                <li><p><strong>WEATHERPROOF COAT</strong><br>Do you need a foolproof plan to stay warm this winter? A weatherproof coat is made of water-resistant and windproof materials to protect you from the elements. What are the different types of weatherproof coats? A hard-shell coat features a waterproof and windproof design that has limited breathability. They are great for skiing and snowboarding. A soft-shell coat features a water-resistant design that is breathable and moisture wicking. These coats are best for climbing. Whether you&rsquo;re hitting the slopes or braving a blizzard, a weatherproof coat will keep you toasty in tough conditions.</p></li>
                <li><p><strong>DOWN COAT</strong><br>What are the benefits of a down coat? A down coat has a great warmth-to-weight ratio, so it keeps you warm while being lightweight. Since they can be stowed away easily in a packable pouch, down coats are perfect for those engaging in outdoor activities, like hiking, climbing and skiing. How do you stay warmer while you&rsquo;re out and about? Scope out down coats with drawstrings that tighten to keep the cold air out. Whether you&rsquo;re walking to work or scaling mountains, shore up your winter gear with a down coat.</p></li>
